    - linear and nonlinear restoring forces,
    - damping and nonlinear damping,
    - coupling terms between position and velocity,
    - time-dependent forcing with harmonics,
    - quadratic and cubic cross terms.

    Model form:
        y = params[0] 
            + params[1]*x0                 # linear time term (forcing or drift)
            + params[2]*x1                 # linear restoring force (-ω² * x)
