        + params[6] * (x2 ** 3)           # cubic velocity nonlinearity
        + params[7] * x1 * x2             # cross term coupling position and velocity nonlinearly
        + params[8] * (x1 ** 4)           # quartic restoring force for stronger nonlinearity in position
        + params[9] * (x1 ** 2) * x2      # quadratic position times velocity coupling term
        + params[10] * (x0 ** 2) * x1     # quadratic time-position interaction term 
        + params[11] * (x0 ** 3) * x2     # cubic time-velocity interaction term 
    )
    
    return y
