    - quartic term in velocity (v^4) to model higher order damping or forcing effects,
    - additional cross terms between position and velocity including cubic-quartic interactions,
    - time-position quadratic cross term to model possible time-dependent stiffness changes,
    - retains all lower order terms from v1.

    Parameters:
    - params: array-like with at least 16 elements:
        params[0]: constant offset term
        params[1]: linear term in time t
        params[2]: linear term in position x
        params[3]: linear term in velocity v
        params[4]: cubic term in position x^3
        params[5]: cubic term in velocity v^3
        params[6]: quadratic cross term x * v
        params[7]: quadratic term in position x^2
        params[8]: quadratic term in velocity v^2
        params[9]: quartic term in position x^4
        params[10]: cubic cross term x^2 * v
        params[11]: time-velocity cross term t * v
        # New terms added below:
        params[12]: quintic term in position x^5
